		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Allegro has issues with newer versions of Visual C++ that may not have been resolved yet. However if you can get an older version like MSVC 6.0, and run it on an older version of windows like XP, you should have no issues. I run Windows XP in a virtual machine and use MSVC 6.0 for Allegro stuff.
<br />
<br />You can also try SDL.

		

