<br />
<br />There's also <a href="http://www.lazyfoo.net/SDL_tutorials/index.php" class="postlink">all these.</a> if you want some little tutorials on SDL, but you could probably get as far just reading the documentation.
<br />
<br /><a href="http://www.lazyfoo.net/SDL_tutorials/lesson03/index.php" class="postlink">This one</a> deals with how to include extension SDL libraries. I hope that helps.

		

